      <title>摩尔多瓦总统赢得选举 重振加入欧盟势头</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/moldova-s-pro-eu-president-headed-for-victory-in-key-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩尔多瓦总统玛雅·桑杜周日在该前苏联加盟共和国的选举中取得决定性胜利，无视俄罗斯干扰选举的努力，并重新推动该国在 2020 年前加入欧盟的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-03/moldova-s-pro-eu-president-headed-for-victory-in-key-election</guid>
